Versi�n de motor anti-virus:3
Versi�n de motor antivirus:5.0.1.85
Versi�n de archivo DAT de firma de anti-virus 915051681
Versi�n de motor de protecci�n contra programas esp�a:5.0.189.0
Versi�n de archivo DAT de firma de protecci�n contra programas esp�a 01.200801.3195
Versi�n de AntiSpam 5.0.6.8903


------------------------------------------------------
Vulnerability

The vulnerability is caused because the program can not analyze very long paths.
This causes a buffer overflow with the possibility of execution of code.

The flaw could be exploited by malware to leave without protection to the system for instance.
	
